  "ciliary_role": "Outher dynein arm intermediate chain protein. D I and D I2 form a complex essential for the stability of both proteins during early stages of outer dynein arms assembly (29113992). Essential for axonemal assembly of the ODA heavy chains D H5 and D H9 (18950741). Required for ODA formation in Kupffer's Vesicle cilia and controls the stablishment of left-right doby axis and kidney formation through regulation of ciliary motility.(20709053, 20707998)",
